  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies drill-down and node viewing mode for an <see cref="T:system.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesigner" />, such as Flowcharts, that are used to compose activities.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 Drilling down into the UI elements is allowed by default. It can be disallowed by setting the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AllowDrillIn%2A> property to `false`. Child nodes are not always collapsed by default, but can be set to always collapse by setting the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AlwaysCollapseChildren%2A> property to `true`.  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
